{
  "texts": [
    "And only then would you say \"That sounds interesting!",
    "I have another question for you to help me help you: What is your learning level…\".",
    "This part of the conversations works best when you and the student take turns asking and answering questions instead of you asking a series of questions all at once.",
    "That way you can have more of a natural dialogue.",
    "• What would you like to learn about and why?"
  ]
}